&lt;a href=&#34;https://shoka.lostyu.me/computer-science/note/theme-shoka-doc/display/&#34; title=&#34;Click Me&#34;&gt;shoka&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/blinkfox/hexo-theme-matery/blob/develop/README_CN.md&#34; title=&#34;matery&#34;&gt;matery&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;new&lt;br&gt;
